high_descs: Turn around and walk ahead to the fridge.
Take the plate out of the freezer compartment of the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Place the plate on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed plate on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge then turn left to face it.
Open the freezer and grab the black plate then close the door.
Turn around and walk to the stove that's in front of you to your left.
Look up and warm the plate in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Move a small step to your left.
Put the plate under the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Pick up the black plate from inside the fridge on the top shelf on the right and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the white stove on the right.
Put the plate inside the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it, and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the small counter to the right next to the stove.
Put the heated plate on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on a counter.
